latestIgtvVideos.title: US Army Veteran Receives Powered Wheelchair
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🇺🇸 Happy Veterans Day🇺🇸 Our 2nd Annual Crunch for a Vet ceremony where we presented a custom pink camo Freedom Mobility 6×6 all-terrain power wheelchair to Long Island veteran, Erin Holmes. This power wheelchair will allow U.S. Army Specialist, Erin Holmes, to have more mobility and independence as well as keep up with her growing family
.
We thank everyone that has supported and participated in our Crunch For A Vet Challenge. With your help we were able to make a difference❤️
#crunchforavet  #fitcrunch  #veteransday
